  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of Tripterygium Wilfordii in Patients With Rheumatoid Arthritis</brief_title>
  <acronym>TRIFRA</acronym>
  <official_title>Evaluation of Oral T2 (Chloroform/Methanol Extract of Tripterygium Wilfordii Hook F) in the Treatment of RA Patients With Clinical Efficacy and Safety.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
