  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Evaluation of oral T2 (chloroform/methanol extract of Tripterygium wilfordii Hook F) in the
      treatment of RA patients with clinical efficacy and safety.Open-labeled, randomized,
      prospective multi-center clinical trial. Observation period of 24 weeks.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
